OL,3,CMother speaks of relief as son's
OL,4,Cmedication becomes available on NHS
OL,6,FAnila Dhami went to meet the family
OL,7,Fand hear about what this breakthrough
OL,8,Fmeans.
OL,10,FA mother who was spending thousands of
OL,11,Fpounds a month on medication to treat
OL,12,Fher son's brain tumour has spoken of
OL,13,Fher relief after the drug became
OL,14,Favailable on the NHS.
OL,16,FThe combination of dabrafenib and
OL,17,Ftrametinib was approved for NHS use
OL,18,Ffor youngsters with brain tumours in
OL,19,FApril.
