OL,6,FThe two drugs work together by
OL,7,Fblocking the growth signal coming from
OL,8,Fthe mutant BRAF protein and can slow
OL,9,For even stop the tumour from growing.
OL,11,FMrs Josephs described her son as
OL,12,F"perfectly fit and healthy, really
OL,13,Fstrong and really into sports" before
OL,14,Fhis first seizure at age six in
OL,15,FSeptember 2020, during the Covid-19
OL,16,Fpandemic.
OL,18,F"Mum's sleep with one eye open,"
OL,19,Fexplained Ms Josephs.
