OL,6,F"It was in the middle of the night and
OL,7,FI just hard these noises so I went
OL,8,Finto this room and he was having a
OL,9,Ffull seizure."
OL,11,FHis family called an ambulance, and
OL,12,Fdoctors decided to do an MRI as a
OL,13,Fprecaution.
OL,15,FDoctors initially thought the seizure
OL,16,Fwas a one-off and Alexander was booked
OL,17,Fin for a routine MRI on his brain,
OL,18,Fwhich took place in the November.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/19
