OL,6,F"I think we met with them three or
OL,7,Ffour days before Christmas. so
OL,8,Feverything shuts down, I asked for
OL,9,Felective surgery so the day after
OL,10,Fboxing day I phoned up and said I feel
OL,11,Fstrongly if it can come out it should
OL,12,Fcome out," she said.
OL,14,FWeeks later Alexander's cancer was
OL,15,Fconfirmed as an aggressive glioma
OL,16,Fwhich had grown.
OL,18,FAlexander eventually had a 10-hour
OL,19,Foperation to remove the tumour in
OL,20,FMarch 2021, when it was discovered the
OL,21,Fcancer had spread to his spine.
