OL,3,CMother speaks of relief as son's
OL,4,Cmedication becomes available on NHS
OL,6,F"They knew it wasn't behaving like a
OL,7,Flower-grade tumour," she continued.
OL,9,F"After they removed it completely,
OL,10,Fthey saw the lesions on the spine,
OL,11,Fthey thought they'd wait to see and
OL,12,Faim to remove the lesions on the
OL,13,Fspine, but within the weeks, he
OL,14,Fstarted seizing again and the brain
OL,15,Ftumour returned within weeks."
OL,17,FHis second and third surgeries taking
OL,18,Fplace in June of that year.
