OL,6,F"We just tried to stay positive, and
OL,7,Fkeep everyone positive. Just tried to
OL,8,Fexplain things to them in child-
OL,9,Ffriendly ways as we went along," said
OL,10,FMs Josephs.
OL,12,F"We were going through surgeries and
OL,13,Fthen six weeks of daily radiotherapy
OL,14,Fto his whole head and spine, he was so
OL,15,Funwell. He lost weight and lost his
OL,16,Fhair, he was hospitalised many times
OL,17,Ffor uncontrollable illness because of
OL,18,Fthe harsh treatment."
