OL,6,FThe medication came as a relief after
OL,7,Fthe family spoke to doctors all around
OL,8,Fthe world.
OL,10,FMrs Josephs explained: "We researched
OL,11,Fand researched, I reached out to
OL,12,Ffamily friends, looking for trials all
OL,13,Faround the world and we spoke to
OL,14,Fdoctors all around the world.
OL,16,F"It was actually a doctor in America,
OL,17,Fa world leader on paediatric brain
OL,18,Ftumours, and the doctors here in the
OL,19,FUK, they all work together.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/19
