OL,6,F"They put forward this medication.
OL,7,FWhilst it was in a trial the data was
OL,8,Freally good and they recommended that
OL,9,Fhe take it straight after radio
OL,10,Ftherapy.
OL,12,F"He was the first child in the UK to
OL,13,Fhave it straight after radiotherapy -
OL,14,Fbecause Xander's was considered so
OL,15,Faggressive, they thought it was life
OL,16,For death and he needed to access is
OL,17,Fstraight away."
OL,19,FThe medication wasn't available on the
OL,20,FNHS so the family began fundraising.
