OL,6,F"We had a really good response, but we
OL,7,Fdidn't get to our target just through
OL,8,Fthat alone and that point, I broke
OL,9,Fdown," said Mrs Josephs.
OL,11,F"It just felt so enormous, the amounts
OL,12,Fof money and Xander was so unwell,
OL,13,Fjust coping with everything and
OL,14,Fputting Xander and our other son
OL,15,Ffirst. The fundraising felt like an
OL,16,Fimpossible task."
