OL,6,FIt was thanks to a group of mothers
OL,7,Fwho got behind the family and helped
OL,8,Forganise events to raise money for the
OL,9,Fmedication. These events included
OL,10,Fmarathons, climbing mountains and
OL,11,Fjumping out planes.
OL,13,FAlexander's school also did sponsored
OL,14,Ffun-runs, and sponsored zip lines -
OL,15,Fsomething both him and his brother got
OL,16,Finvolved in.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/19
