OL,6,F"It was a lot of work, but thankfully
OL,7,FI had four amazing women behind me to
OL,8,Fdo it, and when I needed to look after
OL,9,FXander, they just stepped forward.
OL,10,FThey have children of their own and
OL,11,Fthey help save him," she added.
OL,13,FMedics told the family that Alexander
OL,14,Fwas in remission in January 2024,
OL,15,Fleaving Mrs Josephs "cautiously
OL,16,Foptimistic, as he's still undergoing
OL,17,Ftreatment".
OL,19,F"They were words we'd waited to hear,"
OL,20,Fshe added.
