OL,6,F"Alexander is getting back to his
OL,7,Fsports and he's just becoming a normal
OL,8,Flittle boy again. He's doing
OL,9,Fremarkably well.
OL,11,F"He's just getting his life back. I
OL,12,Fdon't want to say he's unscathed
OL,13,Fbecause he's not.
OL,15,F"But it could have been so much worse.
OL,16,FWe're really grateful for how he's
OL,17,Fdoing."
OL,19,FThe family now plan to enjoy summer,
OL,20,FMrs Josephs said: "The weather is
OL,21,Fdefinitely not going to stop us."
