OL,6,FCameron Miller, director of strategy
OL,7,Fand external affairs at the Brain
OL,8,FTumour Charity, said: "Twenty years
OL,9,Fago, our research funding helped
OL,10,Fidentify BRAF mutations in brain
OL,11,Ftumours.
OL,13,F"When a breakthrough came following
OL,14,Fclinical trials, we worked with the
OL,15,FNational Institute for Health and Care
OL,16,FExcellence to ensure the patient voice
OL,17,Fwas heard.
OL,26,@pD@WOUuD@AOU
